Rating: 3
Very yummy -- everyone raved. Make sure you measure the cups of lettuce -- I used two whole heads, and it was way too much, hence sparsely dressed. The bacon took much longer than 5 minutes to get crispy. I also drained much of the bacon fat before cooking the croutons, and they didn't really get crisp, so I broiled them, but they were still a little soft.

