Rating: 4
My guests (who are good friends and are always honest about my cooking) told me that it was the BEST salad they EVER had. I used a Barlett pear instead of the apple; also, I didn't have sherry vinegar on hand, so just used red wine vinegar and added a touch of honey. Be certain to chill your salad bowls beforehand, don't over-dress the greens, and you, too, will be en route to salad heaven. This is a keeper!

